@prefix bao:  <https://w3id.org/boolean-algebra-ontology#>.
@prefix uno:  <https://w3id.org/unique-name-ontology#>.
@prefix rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.
@prefix sh:   <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#>.
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix :   <http://www.example.org#>.


# The triples below assert both that "Mary" and "Sue" denote the same individual in the domain and that they do not. A contradiction is therefore inferred.
:Mary uno:sameAs :Sue.
<<:Mary uno:sameAs :Sue>> rdf:type bao:False.



